<div class="container mt-5">
  <h1 class="text-center mb-4">📝 About This App</h1>

  <p class="lead text-center">
    <strong>TaskFlow</strong> is a simple and intuitive to-do list web application designed to help you stay organized and productive every day. Whether you're managing daily tasks, planning a project, or just trying to stay on top of your goals — TaskFlow has your back.
  </p>

  <hr>

  <h2>✨ Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>✅ Create, edit, and delete tasks with ease</li>
    <li>📅 Set due dates and times</li>
    <li>🚦 Mark tasks as complete or incomplete</li>
    <li>🔒 Secure login and account management using Devise</li>
    <li>📱 Mobile-friendly, responsive design</li>
  </ul>

  <hr>

  <h2>💡 Why Use TaskFlow?</h2>
  <p>
    In today's busy world, staying organized can make a big difference. TaskFlow helps you:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Break down large goals into manageable tasks</li>
    <li>Track your progress over time</li>
    <li>Stay motivated by checking off completed items</li>
    <li>Prioritize what's important</li>
  </ul>

  <hr>

  <h2>👨‍💻 Built With</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Ruby on Rails (Backend Framework)</li>
    <li>Bootstrap 4 (Frontend Styling)</li>
    <li>Devise (User Authentication)</li>
    <li>SQLite (Development Database)</li>
  </ul>
</div>
